#: src/live2d-Utils.php:92
msgid "V1 / V2 模型"
msgstr "V1 vs. V2 models"

#: src/live2d-Utils.php:94
msgid "本插件同时支持两套独立的 Live2D 加载链路。第一次配置前请先确认手里的模型属于哪一类："
msgstr "This plugin ships two completely independent Live2D loaders. Before your first configuration, decide which one your model belongs to:"

#: src/live2d-Utils.php:96
msgid "模型类别"
msgstr "Category"

#: src/live2d-Utils.php:97
msgid "清单文件"
msgstr "Manifest file"

#: src/live2d-Utils.php:98
msgid "主体文件"
msgstr "Main file"

#: src/live2d-Utils.php:99
msgid "对应 API 方式"
msgstr "Matching API mode"

#: src/live2d-Utils.php:101
msgid "V1（Cubism 2 / 3 系，如 22 娘、Pio、Tia、Shizuku 等）"
msgstr "V1 (Cubism 2 / 3 era — 22-Niang, Pio, Tia, Shizuku, etc.)"

#: src/live2d-Utils.php:103
msgid "「本地部署旧版模型」或「自行部署旧版模型」"
msgstr "\"Local legacy models\" or \"Self-hosted legacy models\""

#: src/live2d-Utils.php:104
msgid "Cubism 4+（V2，官方仍在维护的最新格式）"
msgstr "Cubism 4+ (V2 — the format Live2D Inc. is actively maintaining)"

#: src/live2d-Utils.php:106
msgid "「自定义模型路径（Cubism 4+）」（需登录并购买授权）"
msgstr "\"Custom model path (Cubism 4+)\" (requires sign-in and a paid license)"

#: src/live2d-Utils.php:108
msgid "简单判断：清单文件名以 .model3.json 结尾就是 V2，否则是 V1。"
msgstr "Quick check: if the manifest filename ends with .model3.json it is V2, otherwise it is V1."

#: src/live2d-Utils.php:115
msgid "API 方式与模型路径"
msgstr "API mode and model path"

#: src/live2d-Utils.php:117
msgid "「API 方式」是 V1 / V2 链路的总开关，三个选项作用不同："
msgstr "\"API mode\" is the master switch between the V1 and V2 loaders. The three options behave differently:"

#: src/live2d-Utils.php:119
#: src/waifu-Settings-Base.php:143
msgid "本地部署旧版模型"
msgstr "Local legacy models"

#: src/live2d-Utils.php:119
msgid "使用插件随包内置的 V1 模型，由本站 REST 接口（/wp-json/live2d/v1/model/*）提供，不向外网发起请求。「模型 ID」「材质 ID」会自动变成下拉框。需要在「Live 2D 创意工坊」页面先把模型下载到本地。"
msgstr "Use the V1 models bundled with the plugin. They are served by your own site over /wp-json/live2d/v1/model/*, with no outbound requests. \"Model ID\" and \"Texture ID\" turn into dropdowns. Download the model first from the \"Live 2D Workshop\" page."

#: src/live2d-Utils.php:120
#: src/waifu-Settings-Base.php:152
msgid "自行部署旧版模型"
msgstr "Self-hosted legacy models"

#: src/live2d-Utils.php:120
msgid "对接您自己服务器或第三方提供的 V1 模型 API（即 fghrsh 风格接口），「模型 API」需要填写返回 model_list.json 的接口根地址。"
msgstr "Connect to a V1 model API hosted on your own server or a third party (the fghrsh-style API). \"Model API\" must point to the root URL that returns model_list.json."

#: src/live2d-Utils.php:121
#: src/waifu-Settings-Base.php:159
#: src/waifu-Settings-Base.php:167
msgid "自定义模型路径（Cubism 4+）"
msgstr "Custom model path (Cubism 4+)"

#: src/live2d-Utils.php:121
msgid "用于 Cubism 4+ 模型（V2，*.model3.json）。需要登录账号并完成付费后才能选择。"
msgstr "For Cubism 4+ models (V2, *.model3.json). Available only after signing in and purchasing a license."

#: src/live2d-Utils.php:123
msgid "「模型 API」何时以 .json 结尾、何时以斜杠结尾"
msgstr "When \"Model API\" should end with .json vs. with a trailing slash"

#: src/live2d-Utils.php:124
msgid "仅当「API 方式 = 自定义模型路径（Cubism 4+）」时，「模型 API」支持以下两种写法，由结尾字符决定走哪种："
msgstr "Only when \"API mode = Custom model path (Cubism 4+)\" is selected does \"Model API\" accept the two formats below. The trailing character decides which one is used:"

#: src/live2d-Utils.php:126
msgid "写法"
msgstr "Format"

#: src/live2d-Utils.php:127
msgid "行为"
msgstr "Behaviour"

#: src/live2d-Utils.php:128
msgid "「模型目录」是否使用"
msgstr "Is \"Model directory\" used?"

#: src/live2d-Utils.php:130
msgid "以 .json 结尾（直链单模型）"
msgstr "Ends with .json (direct link to a single model)"

#: src/live2d-Utils.php:131
msgid "直接当作 *.model3.json 加载，不再做任何路径拼接。例：https://cdn.example.com/live2d/haru/haru.model3.json"
msgstr "Loaded as a *.model3.json directly, with no further path concatenation. Example: https://cdn.example.com/live2d/haru/haru.model3.json"

#: src/live2d-Utils.php:132
msgid "忽略，下方「模型目录」「待机动画文件名」两行会自动隐藏。"
msgstr "Ignored — the \"Model directory\" and \"Idle motion filename\" rows below are hidden automatically."

#: src/live2d-Utils.php:133
msgid "以 / 结尾（目录根 + 多模型）"
msgstr "Ends with / (directory root + multiple models)"

#: src/live2d-Utils.php:134
msgid "当作根目录使用，配合下方「模型目录」每行一个名称，自动按 {模型 API}{名称}/{名称}.model3.json 拼成完整 URL。"
msgstr "Treated as a root directory. Combined with the \"Model directory\" list below (one name per line), the full URL is assembled as {Model API}{name}/{name}.model3.json."

#: src/live2d-Utils.php:135
msgid "必填。每行写一个子目录名称，名称必须与 {名称}.model3.json 的前缀完全一致。"
msgstr "Required. Put one sub-directory name per line; the name must match the prefix of {name}.model3.json exactly."

#: src/live2d-Utils.php:137
msgid "补充约束：路径不能包含中文；HTTPS 站点的模型清单及其引用到的所有资源（.moc3、贴图、motion3.json、physics3.json 等）也必须是 HTTPS；放在第三方对象存储 / CDN 时请正确开启 CORS。"
msgstr "Additional constraints: paths must not contain non-ASCII characters; on HTTPS sites the manifest and every referenced asset (.moc3, textures, motion3.json, physics3.json, etc.) must also be HTTPS; if hosted on third-party object storage / CDN, enable CORS for your site origin."

#: src/live2d-Utils.php:138
msgid "「默认材质 ID」仅 V1 模型使用，V2 模型留空即可。"
msgstr "\"Default texture ID\" is used only by V1 models — leave it blank for V2."

#: src/live2d-Utils.php:145
#: src/waifu-Settings-Base.php:97
msgid "模型防盗保护（Cubism 4+）"
msgstr "Model anti-leech protection (Cubism 4+)"

#: src/live2d-Utils.php:147
msgid "「模型防盗保护（Cubism 4+）」只对 Cubism 4+ 模型（自定义模型路径）生效，旧版模型（本地 / 自行部署旧版）走站内接口，本身不需要这层保护。"
msgstr "\"Model anti-leech protection (Cubism 4+)\" applies only to Cubism 4+ models (Custom model path). Legacy models (local / self-hosted legacy) are served by your own site and do not need this layer."

#: src/live2d-Utils.php:149
#: src/waifu-Settings-Base.php:261
msgid "不缓存 (默认)"
msgstr "Do not cache (default)"

#: src/live2d-Utils.php:149
msgid "插件不动您填的「模型 API」，浏览器直接拉源站。适用于您已经把模型放在阿里云 OSS、腾讯云 COS、又拍、七牛、自家 CDN 等已经具备 Referer 防盗 / URL 鉴权能力的存储上。"
msgstr "The plugin keeps your \"Model API\" untouched and the browser fetches directly from origin. Suitable when your model is hosted on Alibaba OSS, Tencent COS, Upyun, Qiniu, your own CDN, or any storage that already supports Referer / URL-signing protection."

#: src/live2d-Utils.php:150
#: src/waifu-Settings-Base.php:267
msgid "缓存到本地 (推荐)"
msgstr "Cache to local (recommended)"

#: src/live2d-Utils.php:150
msgid "插件会把模型涉及的全部文件下载到本站 wp-content/plugins/live-2d/model/ 下，并对前端只露出经过签名的临时 URL，访客 F12 也看不到源站地址。适用于源站没有防盗能力（GitHub Pages、jsDelivr、自建 nginx 等）。"
msgstr "The plugin downloads every model asset under wp-content/plugins/live-2d/model/ on your site and exposes only signed, ephemeral URLs to the front end — visitors cannot see the origin URL even via DevTools. Suitable when the origin lacks anti-leech features (GitHub Pages, jsDelivr, self-hosted nginx, etc.)."

#: src/live2d-Utils.php:152
msgid "选择「缓存到本地」后，下方会出现下载面板：可以「全部下载」一键缓存全部已配置模型，也可以等访客首次访问时由插件后台自动懒下载。「清理孤儿」用于删除已经从设置里移除、但还残留在本地缓存里的旧模型文件。"
msgstr "Selecting \"Cache locally\" exposes a download panel below: use \"Download all\" to cache every configured model in one click, or let the plugin lazily fetch on a visitor's first request. \"Clean orphans\" removes model files that were once configured but are no longer referenced."

#: src/live2d-Utils.php:159
msgid "提示消息与特殊标记"
msgstr "Tip messages and placeholders"

#: src/live2d-Utils.php:163
msgid "在「高级设置」「提示消息选项」页面点击 %s 可以在同一个事件下追加随机语句，运行时随机选一条显示。"
msgstr "In the \"Advanced settings\" or \"Tip message options\" page, click %s to add another random sentence to the same event; one of them is picked at random at runtime."

#: src/live2d-Utils.php:166
msgid "以下事件支持在文本中插入特殊标记，运行时会被替换为对应内容："
msgstr "These events support placeholders that get replaced at runtime:"

#: src/live2d-Utils.php:168
msgid "鼠标悬停时的消息提示：{text} 触发事件的内容、{highlight} 高亮样式占位符"
msgstr "Mouse hover tip: {text} the triggering content, {highlight} the highlight-style placeholder"

#: src/live2d-Utils.php:169
msgid "鼠标点击时的消息提示：{text} 触发事件的内容、{highlight} 高亮样式占位符"
msgstr "Mouse click tip: {text} the triggering content, {highlight} the highlight-style placeholder"

#: src/live2d-Utils.php:170
msgid "节日事件：{year} 年份、{highlight} 高亮样式占位符"
msgstr "Holiday events: {year} the year, {highlight} the highlight-style placeholder"

#: src/live2d-Utils.php:171
msgid "搜索引擎入站提示：{title} 网站标题、{keyword} 关键词、{website} 站点名称、{highlight} 高亮样式占位符（请以预设值为准，并非所有搜索引擎都会带齐这些信息）"
msgstr "Search-engine referral tip: {title} page title, {keyword} keyword, {website} site name, {highlight} highlight-style placeholder (refer to the defaults — not every search engine provides all of these)."

#: src/live2d-Utils.php:172
msgid "访问本站点的提示：{website} 站点名称、{highlight} 高亮样式占位符"
msgstr "Site visitor tip: {website} site name, {highlight} highlight-style placeholder"

#: src/live2d-Utils.php:173
msgid "一言 API 的消息：{title}、{source}、{creator}、{date}、{dynasty}、{author}、{highlight}（请以预设值为准，并非所有句子都会带齐这些字段）"
msgstr "Hitokoto API message: {title}, {source}, {creator}, {date}, {dynasty}, {author}, {highlight} (refer to the defaults — not every sentence carries all of these fields)."

#: src/live2d-Utils.php:177
msgid "高亮用法：在任意 style 属性中插入 %s 即可，高亮颜色请到「提示消息选项」中设置。"
msgstr "Highlight usage: insert %s into any style attribute; the highlight colour is configured under \"Tip message options\"."

#: src/live2d-Utils.php:180
msgid "如需恢复全部默认值：删除插件后重新安装即可（注意会同时清空已保存的设置）。"
msgstr "To restore every default: uninstall and reinstall the plugin (this also wipes your saved settings)."

#: src/live2d-Utils.php:187
msgid "样式与工具栏"
msgstr "Style and toolbar"

#: src/live2d-Utils.php:190
msgid "「看板娘大小」「页面边距」「拖拽样式」位于「样式设置」页，调整后立即对前端生效。"
msgstr "\"Waifu size\", \"Page padding\" and \"Drag mode\" live on the \"Style settings\" page — changes take effect on the front end immediately."

#: src/live2d-Utils.php:191
msgid "「面页小于指定宽度禁用看板娘」用于在小屏 / 移动端隐藏，留空或填 0 表示始终显示。"
msgstr "\"Hide waifu when the page is narrower than\" hides the waifu on small screens / mobile devices; leave it empty or set 0 to always display."

#: src/live2d-Utils.php:192
msgid "「模型切换方式」「材质切换方式」分别决定按下工具栏切换按钮时是顺序切换还是随机切换。"
msgstr "\"Model switch mode\" and \"Texture switch mode\" decide whether the toolbar buttons cycle sequentially or pick at random."

#: src/live2d-Utils.php:193
msgid "「超采样」与「抗锯齿」属于付费功能，仅对 V2 模型有效，开启后可显著提升贴图清晰度，但会增加 GPU 占用。"
msgstr "\"Super-sampling\" and \"Anti-aliasing\" are paid features that apply only to V2 models. Enabling them noticeably improves texture sharpness at the cost of GPU usage."

#: src/live2d-Utils.php:194
msgid "「Cubism Core for Web 引用地址」一般保留默认（指向插件随包分发的 6.x 本地副本即可）。除非您明确知道在做什么，不建议改成 CDN 地址，官方 CDN 目前仍停留在 5.1.0，会与插件内置 Framework 不兼容。"
msgstr "\"Cubism Core for Web URL\" is best left at the default value (pointing to the bundled 6.x local copy). Avoid switching to a CDN unless you know what you're doing — the official CDN is still on 5.1.0 and is incompatible with the bundled Framework."

#: src/live2d-Utils.php:202
msgid "进阶文档与链接"
msgstr "Further reading and links"

#: src/live2d-Utils.php:205
msgid "V1 / V2 模型详细对比"
msgstr "Detailed V1 vs. V2 comparison"

#: src/live2d-Utils.php:206
msgid "使用 V2 自定义模型（Cubism 4+）"
msgstr "Using a custom V2 model (Cubism 4+)"

#: src/live2d-Utils.php:207
msgid "V2 模型防盗链详解"
msgstr "V2 anti-leech protection in depth"

#: src/live2d-Utils.php:208
msgid "V2 模型的触摸区域 (HitArea)"
msgstr "Touch areas (HitArea) on V2 models"

#: src/live2d-Utils.php:209
msgid "ChatGPT 接入与自定义 API"
msgstr "ChatGPT integration and custom APIs"

#: src/live2d-Utils.php:210
msgid "Chrome / Edge 浏览器扩展（个人用户）"
msgstr "Chrome / Edge browser extension (personal users)"

#: src/live2d-Utils.php:212
msgid "源码与 issue 反馈："
msgstr "Source code and issue tracker:"

#: src/live2d-Utils.php:228
msgid "创意工坊使用说明"
msgstr "Workshop instructions"

#: src/live2d-Utils.php:230
msgid "本页面列出插件内置的 V1（Cubism 2 / 3 系）模型，例如 bilibili 22 娘 / 33 娘、Potion Maker Pio / Tia、Shizuku 等。点击「下载」后，插件会从作者维护的源站把模型 ZIP 拉到本站、解压到 wp-content/plugins/live-2d/model/ 目录中。"
msgstr "This page lists the V1 (Cubism 2 / 3 era) models bundled with the plugin — bilibili 22-Niang / 33-Niang, Potion Maker Pio / Tia, Shizuku, and so on. Clicking \"Download\" pulls the ZIP from the author's origin and extracts it into wp-content/plugins/live-2d/model/."

#: src/live2d-Utils.php:231
msgid "使用要求："
msgstr "Requirements:"

#: src/live2d-Utils.php:233
msgid "已经在 live2dweb.com 完成账号登录，并把账号 Key 保存到「Live 2D 设置 → 登录」选项卡。"
msgstr "Signed in on live2dweb.com and saved your account Key under \"Live 2D Settings → Sign in\"."

#: src/live2d-Utils.php:234
